      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-a" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio${action:Talk}<BR>I have finished creating the altar, and the ritual has also started smoothly.<BR>There aren't any problems yet, but...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-b" mid="52" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Apa yang kamu pikirkan?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-c" mid="53" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>Actually... There must be a <FONT color=#a82424>Scroll</FONT> to handle great powers for a big ritual. The scroll that I have right now has modified the way of the Ancients to fit the humans, so it is not enough to suit a big ritual.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-d" mid="55" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hmm... Oh begitu.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-d" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300027" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-e" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>That's why I will need the <FONT color=#a82424>Ancient's Scroll</FONT>. A scroll that has been used for the important rituals of the Ancients, should be enough to withstand the powers of the giant Sea Monster.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-f" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Dimana aku dapat menemukan itu?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-f" image="QW_41.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-g" mid="59" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>At <FONT color=#a82424>Explosion zone in Withered Leaves Forest</FONT>. It is a devastated place where all life forms have been lost because of some kind of an experiment that has been conducted by the Ancients. Therefore it has been said that a scroll of great powers should still be remaining somewhere in the area.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-g" image="QW_41.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-h" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Kalau begitu, bukankah itu berarti barang tersebut berbahaya?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-i" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>It depends on who and what somebody uses it for. You cannot forget that powers are merely a tool. If one is truly concerned about the safety of Saint's Haven, then the one should certainly be able to handle such powers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-j" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Itu terdengar masuk akal.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-j" image="QW_41.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Bishop.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n039_bishop_ignasio-1-" mid="65" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Bishop Ignacio$<BR>The strongest monster at <FONT color=#a82424>Explosion zone in Withered Leaves Forest</FONT> should be holding onto that scroll, so look carefully. I'm counting on you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
